Introduction

The rapid growth of digital learning has transformed education by making quality resources accessible anytime and anywhere. This EdTech app provides students with interactive courses, quizzes, progress tracking, and personalized learning experiences to enhance engagement and academic performance.

Problem Statement

Traditional learning methods often lack flexibility, personalization, and continuous assessment. Students face difficulties in organizing study materials, tracking progress, and receiving immediate feedback. This platform addresses these challenges by providing a centralized and interactive learning environment.

Objectives

• Provide easy access to educational content.
• Enable self-paced learning through video lessons and quizzes.
• Track learning progress and achievements.
• Improve student engagement through gamification.
• Offer personalized learning experiences.

Target Audience

• School students (Classes 10–12)
• College students
• Competitive exam aspirants
• Lifelong learners

Features

Student Features

• User Registration and Login
• Browse Courses by Subject
• Video Lessons and Study Materials
• Quizzes and Assessments
• Progress Tracking Dashboard
• Learning Streaks and Achievements
• Profile Management
• Notifications and Reminders

Smart Features

• AI Study Assistant
• Personalized Course Recommendations
• Performance Analytics
• Certificate Generation

Technologies Used

Frontend
• Figma
• React Native / Flutter

Backend
• Node.js / Python

Database
• Firebase / MongoDB

Additional Tools
• AI APIs for chatbot assistance
• Cloud Storage for learning materials

Benefits

• Learn anytime and anywhere.
• Personalized and interactive learning experience.
• Better progress monitoring.
• Increased motivation through rewards and achievements.
• Reduced dependency on traditional classrooms.

Future Scope

• Live classes and video conferencing
• Peer discussion forums
• AR/VR-based learning experiences
• Multi-language support
• Advanced AI tutors and adaptive learning

Conclusion

The EdTech app aims to create an engaging and personalized learning ecosystem that helps students learn effectively through digital resources, assessments, and progress monitoring. By integrating modern technologies and AI-driven features, the platform enhances accessibility and improves educational outcomes.
